description.en:
Singapore TOO Fund Management Company was established in 2021, focusing on blockchain technology investment and virtual currency mining.

TOO is committed to discover and explore new ventures, while acquiring and cooperating with a public YouTube channel. TOO fund-related financial channels will also be launched. TOO will gradually launch its own decentralized exchanges, public chains and steadily advancing its ecosystem structure. TOO is currently negotiating with the Lao government to reach a 50MW hydropower project to assist the development of a self-operated to manage Ethereum, Bitcoin mining machines, and other businesses.
